N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8000.3 - Qualifying highway

State Regulations

Qualifying highways are those highways on the national system
of interstate and defense highways and Federal-aid primary system highways that
are designated by the Commissioner of Transportation in this Chapter as
qualifying highways. Notes
